---
description: "Audit trail and compliance tracking rules"
globs: ["**/*.py", "**/*.ts"]
alwaysApply: false
---

## Audit Trail
- Log all state transitions with timestamp and actor.
- Include previous and next state in audit events.
- Retain audit logs for minimum 90 days.

## Compliance
- All review actions require explicit authorization.
- Failed access attempts must be logged.
- Export audit logs in JSON format.